column2: SELECT TOP #  p.ra,p.dec,s.veldisp, s.veldisperr,s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass,s.z,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.lnLDeV_g, p.lnLstar_g,p.lnLexp_g,p.fracdev_g,   m.mstellar_median, m.mstellar_err,  ext.bptclass,  ext.oh_p1#, ext.oh_p5#, ext.oh_p8#,   ext.lgm_tot_p1#, ext.lgm_tot_p5#, ext.lgm_tot_p8#,  ext.sfr_tot_p1#, ext.sfr_tot_p5#, ext.sfr_tot_p8#,  ext.specsfr_tot_p1#, ext.specsfr_tot_p5#, ext.specsfr_tot_p8#,   indx.d4#_n, indx.d4#_n_err,  line.h_alpha_flux, line.h_alpha_flux_err,  line.h_beta_flux, line.h_beta_flux_err,   line.oiii_#_flux, line.oiii_#_flux_err,  line.nii_#_flux, line.nii_#_flux_err,  line.nii_#_flux, line.nii_#_flux_err FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN specobjall AS s on s.bestobjID = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS m ON m.specobjid = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ext on ext.specObjID = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecLine As line on line.specObjID = s.specobjid  JOIN galSpecIndx As indx on indx.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE   s.class = &&& and s.subclass = &&& and   s.veldisperr > # and s.veldisp > #*s.veldisperr and  line.h_alpha_flux_err > # and line.h_alpha_flux > #* line.h_alpha_flux_err and  line.h_beta_flux_err > # and line.h_beta_flux > line.h_beta_flux_err and  line.oiii_#_flux_err > # and line.oiii_#_flux > #*line.oiii_#_flux_err and  line.nii_#_flux_err > # and line.nii_#_flux > #*line.nii_#_flux_err and  line.nii_#_flux_err > # and line.nii_#_flux > #*line.nii_#_flux_err
